{"tid":2505694,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"沙田男子駕駛電動滑板車被警方拘捕","createTime":"2021-04-26T22:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T23:49:37.000Z","uid":230530,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cdca84072fe1cc568e73f35cb5647a7818a74a","tid":2505694,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:37:17.000Z","msg":"警方昨晚在沙田水廠街截查1名駕駛電動滑板車的30歲男子時，對方嘗試逃離現場，並駕駛電動滑板車撞向警員，警員其後將他制服及拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n經初步調查，被捕男子涉嫌駕駛未有登記車輛、駕駛時沒有駕駛執照、沒有第三者保險而使用車輛、駕駛時沒有戴上認可防護頭盔、狂亂駕駛及襲警，被警方扣查。被捕男子及警員都報稱不適，送往威爾斯醫院治理。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389000&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6w1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=afea69b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389000</a>"},{"pid":"2ff879ac575917f8cf165b94efc9f5cf2c5d0cf7","tid":2505694,"uid":111644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:38:17.000Z","msg":"駕駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84071ad7220a1e7a92df56a4820d2f8c70d6ad60","tid":2505694,"uid":111644,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:39:37.000Z","msg":"電動滑板車要邊個車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1，2得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cc72a6f0b4bce92f9ed518b7b7a230384c4d56","tid":2505694,"uid":143269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:40:01.000Z","msg":"單車都走得甩 <br />\n<br />\n電動滑板走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b11c4bc0c1ee9d8db0755154212bbbbddaf3d6","tid":2505694,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:41:10.000Z","msg":"其實點解唔比揸<img src=\"/asse